==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Magian
<hw>Ma"gi*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the Magi, or priests of the
Zoroastrian religion in Persia; an adherent of the Zoroastrian
religion.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Ma"gi*an*ism</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Magic</ent>⟦br⟧
